<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,285]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555">
The genus 
<emphasis box="[325,464,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="555">Lobothyreus</emphasis>
Mayr, 
<number box="[548,604,151,176]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" value="1864.0">1864</number>
contains six described species of which currently four are considered as valid (
<bibRefCitation author="Kirkaldy" box="[223,392,188,213]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" refString="Kirkaldy, G. W. (1909) Catalogue of the Hemiptera (Heteroptera) with biological and anatomical references, lists of foodplants and parasites, etc. Vol. I. Cimicidae. F. L. Dames, Berlin, xl + 392 pp." type="book" year="1909">
Kirkaldy 
<number box="[333,392,188,212]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" value="1909.0">1909</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Breddin" box="[405,564,188,213]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" refString="Breddin, G. (1914) Neue oder wenig gekannte neotropische Hemiptera. Abhandlungen Herausgegeben von der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft, 36 (1), 53 - 59." type="journal article" year="1914">
Breddin 
<number box="[504,564,188,212]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" value="1914.0">1914</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). A revision of the genus is currently in preparation by JEE in collaboration with A. Barcellos. 
<emphasis box="[362,614,224,248]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="555">Lobothyreus breviceps</emphasis>
is therefore tentatively recognized as a valid species in the present paper. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,380,260,285]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555">Current status.</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[387,639,260,284]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="555">Lobothyreus breviceps</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Breddin" box="[646,810,260,285]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" refString="Breddin, G. (1914) Neue oder wenig gekannte neotropische Hemiptera. Abhandlungen Herausgegeben von der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft, 36 (1), 53 - 59." type="journal article" year="1914">
Breddin, 
<number box="[751,810,260,284]" pageId="4" pageNumber="555" value="1914.0">1914</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, valid species.
</paragraph>
